				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Speak to Thindo Vintervur - S_GLO_IronThrone_Group5_Prisoner1 08ed18ea-c679-4845-93ab-a88fe73a2e55 - (-13; 37; 20)  in the Dock warehouse after saving them.\r\n\r\nQuick setup:\r\n- Load CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use Debug Book (Ctrl + Shift + 9)\r\n- Set Quest Flags and Options -> Act3 (LOW) -> Iron Throne -> Change State -> Back At Docks -> MajoritySaved\r\n- Then talk to the NPC"
